(self.webpackChunkcheatsheet=self.webpackChunkcheatsheet||[]).push([[3579],{6878:(e,n,a)=>{"use strict";a.r(n),a.d(n,{data:()=>s});const s={key:"v-7a16e276",path:"/sql/table/drop/",title:"DROP TABLE",lang:"en-US",frontmatter:{},excerpt:"",headers:[{level:2,title:"DROP table with foreign key",slug:"drop-table-with-foreign-key",children:[]}],filePathRelative:"sql/table/drop/README.md",git:{updatedTime:162676698e4,contributors:[]}}},5161:(e,n,a)=>{"use strict";a.r(n),a.d(n,{default:()=>t});const s=(0,a(6252).uE)('<h1 id="drop-table" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#drop-table" aria-hidden="true">#</a> DROP TABLE</h1><p>Drop table will <strong>delete the table</strong></p><div class="language-sql ext-sql line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-sql"><code><span class="token keyword">DROP</span> <span class="token keyword">TABLE</span> <span class="token punctuation">[</span>table_name<span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div><h2 id="drop-table-with-foreign-key" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#drop-table-with-foreign-key" aria-hidden="true">#</a> DROP table with foreign key</h2><p>In the normal <code>drop</code>, there is no foreign key to worried about. But when you need to drop a table that have a foreign key constraint, the <strong>Reference Integrity Constraint</strong> comes in. So we need to revoke the constraint check for a while</p><div class="language-sql ext-sql line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-sql"><code><span class="token keyword">SET</span> FOREIGN_KEY_CHECKS <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>\n<span class="token keyword">DROP</span> <span class="token keyword">TABLE</span> employee<span class="token punctuation">;</span>\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br></div></div><p>and do not forget to turn the check on</p><div class="language-sql ext-sql line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-sql"><code><span class="token keyword">SET</span> FOREIGN_KEY_CHECKS <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div>',8),t={render:function(e,n){return s}}}}]);